Job Description

  Implementation and deploying of IT Security Solution (DLP and Endpoints)
  DLP Solution – Forcepoint, McAfee and Digital Guardian
  Endpoint Solutions – McAfee, Trend Micro, Symantec and Sophos
  Liaise with product vendors, partners and customers
  Provide informal training to partners and customers


Requirements

  Diploma/Degree in Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Information Systems or equivalent
  Minimum 2 years of relevant work experience in IT security implementation and deployment
  Minimum 1 year of relevant work experience with DLP and Endpoints Solution
  Good understanding in operating system technology, such as Unix, Linux and Windows Server
  Familiar with Virtualization such as VMWare, Microsoft HyperV, Oracle Box
  Good networking knowledge
  Technically inclined and hands on
  Good interpersonal skills, pro-active and a team player
  Good presentation and writing skills
